A MALAWIborn <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Entrepreneur" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Entrepreneur" target="_blank">entrepreneur</a> who studied at two <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow_Caledonian_University" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow_Caledonian_University" target="_blank">Glasgow</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/University" target="_blank">universities</a> has found huge success with the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_American" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/African_American" target="_blank">African</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nation" target="_blank">nation</a>'s first <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Streaming_media" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Streaming_media" target="_blank">music streaming</a> platformAs we reported in <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/February_1" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/February_1" target="_blank">February</a> Mvelanicom was the creation of <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow_Caledonian_University" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glasgow_Caledonian_University" target="_blank">Glasgow Caledonian University</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graduate_school" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Graduate_school" target="_blank">graduate</a> Dumisani Kapanga who <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Work_of_art" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Work_of_art" target="_blank">works</a> full time as a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finance" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finance" target="_blank">financial</a> analystBut in just three <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Month" target="_blank">months</a> he has secured multiple <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrossCountry" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/CrossCountry" target="_blank">crosscountry</a> deals and more than 5000 <a href="h